    "name": "红移点",
    "steam_appid": 3097370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下文所有画面均为引擎内实时渲染录制（除CG剧情/过场），<strong>无任何预渲染CG与画面合成</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/36b3b492d09fe21ee18227219cee1049.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/36b3b492d09fe21ee18227219cee1049.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/36b3b492d09fe21ee18227219cee1049.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  欢迎加入人类历史上最大的行为艺术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《红移点》是一款融合<strong>现代中国文化</strong>与<strong>后现代荒诞主义</strong>风格的半开放世界动作RPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情发生在2037年内战后的北美。这里不再有超级大国，只有一具流脓发臭的名叫“美利坚”的巨人尸体。扮演不同的势力切入这片自由得过了火的土地，找到“新星特异区”的真相，见证一场关于文明脑死亡的宏大葬礼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>注：本作是单人游戏，但需要联网以启用云端 AI 动态演算/生成（不包含玩家对玩家联机、聊天）。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/bd1c894e4e0c0609a2ac6a8ec538baf3.avif?t=1771073268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras_big/bd1c894e4e0c0609a2ac6a8ec538baf3.webp?t=1771073268 width=1560 height=287 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >美术风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们听够了西方视角下对东方的刻板解构。在《红移点》中，你将体验到一种前所未有的<strong>“中式先锋科幻”</strong>视觉冲击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/b5a634cc0c86b8418f4bbf84d4d9aae5.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/b5a634cc0c86b8418f4bbf84d4d9aae5.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/b5a634cc0c86b8418f4bbf84d4d9aae5.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告别晃眼的霓虹灯与光污染，告别听不懂的故弄玄虚。我们利用独家渲染技术，将<strong>21世纪的中式后赛博工业美学</strong>与<strong>20世纪社会主义美术体系</strong>融合，为你呈现一个<strong>极度写实、冰冷、且充满秩序美感的后赛博世界</strong>。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >嚯嚯这都给我安排上了？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美国红军？南方红脖子？还有新苏联和某大国维和部队？墙上的白发红瞳少女又是怎么回事！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/8ad4e7dd621ce500cfafc069926a8d07.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/8ad4e7dd621ce500cfafc069926a8d07.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/8ad4e7dd621ce500cfafc069926a8d07.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>顶级的视觉表现不意味着燃烧显卡。</strong>我们深知“优化也是美学的一部分”，即便在主流配置下，你依然能身临其境地感受<strong>自由灯塔如何沦为互联网迷因和魔怔思潮的荒诞殖民地</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>（请看下方“配置要求”一栏），普通配置就能玩。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/8ac417c76176d9bb976c91ad724cdec6.avif?t=1771073268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras_big/8ac417c76176d9bb976c91ad724cdec6.webp?t=1771073268 width=1560 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大多数FPS游戏只是在移动一个摄像头，而我们希望玩家<strong>模拟“生存”</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对这群牛鬼蛇神，<strong>批判的武器</strong>是没用的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要用<strong>武器的批判</strong>，给这个病入膏肓的文明做一次物理治疗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实的枪械手感！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/d75802cc32b1f9797283f03467acecf6.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/d75802cc32b1f9797283f03467acecf6.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/d75802cc32b1f9797283f03467acecf6.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射击手感的重点放在<strong>绝对的身临其境</strong>上——<strong>超拟真手感</strong>是我们希望呈现的目标<strong>，</strong>通过拟真视差与复杂的动画融合技术，每一次持枪、奔跑和受击都具备<strong>录像带级的拟真沉浸感</strong>。<strong>我们甚至希望让玩家分不清这是第一人称视频拍摄还是游戏</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，批判的武器不如武器的批判——只有动能、防弹板与肉体的硬碰撞。通过沉浸式的物理反馈，我们希望这不仅是战斗，这是一次精准的“物理治疗”。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >枪匠系统（开发中，少话）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/06eebba6e7fd9cb8c206894043bdc11e.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/06eebba6e7fd9cb8c206894043bdc11e.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/06eebba6e7fd9cb8c206894043bdc11e.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验<strong>细致到螺丝钉级别的建模与拆解</strong>。每一件配件都是具有惯性与碰撞体积的实体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要像真正的武器专家一样，在背包空间、后坐力、重量与人机工效之间寻找微妙的平衡。记住，在这里，哪怕是一个螺丝钉的增减，都会改变你的撤离胜率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/02164d169bb8234fe22471c83b5f99e0.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/02164d169bb8234fe22471c83b5f99e0.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/02164d169bb8234fe22471c83b5f99e0.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几乎每一个单独的配件都可以做出调整<strong>（背包美术还在开发中！——概念设计师注），</strong>改枪时需要权衡重量、后坐力与人机工效，还有背包格子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你站在哪边？我的意思是，Which side you are <span class=\"bb_strike\"> on </span> in?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要让信号丢失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/3cfded287f7a44ffb810f83ed6f8caf3.poster.avif?t=1771073268\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/3cfded287f7a44ffb810f83ed6f8caf3.webm?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097370/extras/3cfded287f7a44ffb810f83ed6f8caf3.mp4?t=1771073268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立刻将《红移点》加入愿望单！</strong></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
